{"tid":2497084,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"卓Sir（卓嘉輝）可以慳返唔洗等喇","createTime":"2021-04-20T09:20:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T13:12:52.000Z","uid":200298,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"9f6420a66866dbadbe61010ab3be7a5255c74d7b","tid":2497084,"uid":200298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T09:20:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbqKsN51WAFnqwZ4RyFKY54hbbaCbHP8R94PM2epyaXZZ?filename=fvd3Ufr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffvd3Ufr.png&h=42c082a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n判終身呀屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無閪屌㗎喇你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUAuJJX5HNMTas8mbsydGkZqZaSyA1PPB5DZpVHPw1hED?filename=ps2z0V7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fps2z0V7.jpg&h=bac3559b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5歲女童遭虐待致死案　生父繼母囚終身　繼外婆囚5年<br />\n<br />\n5歲女童遭虐待致死案，女童生父及繼母早前被裁定謀殺罪成，兩人下午在高等法院依例被判處終身監禁。至於女童繼外婆涉及的兩項殘暴對待兒童罪早前亦裁定罪成，被判監5年。女童父親及繼母早前被控在2018年1月6日謀殺女童，繼外婆則被控於2017年8月至18年1月初，故意虐待和忽略女童和她的兄長。案情透露，女童與父親、繼母搬往繼外婆的住所後，女童長期受到虐待，被藤條毆打、掌摑等，死前曾被多次被拋上天花板撞到頭部，亦曾與事發時8歲的哥哥被迫捱餓。女童在2018年1月6日當日昏迷，父親報警，女童送院時已沒有生命跡象。死因報告指她器官受感染，因敗血病致死，全身有超過130個傷口。<br />\n<br />\n2021-04-20 15:20:34 (3)"},{"pid":"c9cd170b385fbe583514e9854a389ab70700b8bb","tid":2497084,"uid":222970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T09:24:53.000Z","msg":"佢總做緊？"},{"pid":"b32b4a93e7e0c06fbd49c0b0e67ad4bb3baf071b","tid":2497084,"uid":238920,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T09:26:10.000Z","msg":"卓嘉輝係天下第一好老師,唔準你話佢報串屈個細路女"},{"pid":"6492197d9a00a35863a1d6a6220b953f32a31e23","tid":2497084,"uid":268591,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T09:26:25.000Z","msg":"卓Sir自殺死左去係一種解脫"},{"pid":"fef0bdcedbd69f3c7fb5d0051d624060932e0848","tid":2497084,"uid":39710